          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-3-1694182473867-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, transfer the <strong>browned chicken</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray and reserve the pan</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 12-14 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>spiced chicken</strong></p>",
