    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>to a bowl with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and mix until dissolved</p><p>Stir in your <strong>curry powder </strong>and <strong>remaining mayo</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix </strong>to the bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>curried slaw</strong></p>",
